{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/projects/figma-handoff/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"9a0e852a-db9b-547c-bc5c-e83010cec69f","excerpt":"Figma 是一个很棒的设计工具，我使用的这一年来感觉越来越离不开它了。但是，设计从来不是一个人的事，尤其是数字产品的设计。 我们的设计稿，最终要交付到开发手中，让他们来把设计稿变成最终的产品。Figma…","html":"<p>Figma 是一个很棒的设计工具，<a href=\"https://sspai.com/post/55044\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">我使用的这一年来</a>感觉越来越离不开它了。但是，设计从来不是一个人的事，尤其是数字产品的设计。</p>\n<p><strong>我们的设计稿，最终要交付到开发手中，让他们来把设计稿变成最终的产品。</strong>Figma 本身带有交付功能，只需要给开发的账号开通查看权限并发送文件链接就可以了，但是有两个原因导致开发还不太愿意接受 Figma。</p>\n<p>首先，Figma 自身的交付功能还不够强大，只有参考代码。之所以说是参考代码，是因为从设计到代码其实并没有唯一解，开发大概率不会直接复制这段代码直接使用。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c44dcd0de7c3c4b5cbceafad9c794bfd/21482/figma-handoff.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.74999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Figma Handoff\"\n        title=\"Figma Handoff\"\n        src=\"/static/c44dcd0de7c3c4b5cbceafad9c794bfd/6af66/figma-handoff.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c44dcd0de7c3c4b5cbceafad9c794bfd/69538/figma-handoff.png 160w,\n/static/c44dcd0de7c3c4b5cbceafad9c794bfd/72799/figma-handoff.png 320w,\n/static/c44dcd0de7c3c4b5cbceafad9c794bfd/6af66/figma-handoff.png 640w,\n/static/c44dcd0de7c3c4b5cbceafad9c794bfd/d9199/figma-handoff.png 960w,\n/static/c44dcd0de7c3c4b5cbceafad9c794bfd/21b4d/figma-handoff.png 1280w,\n/static/c44dcd0de7c3c4b5cbceafad9c794bfd/21482/figma-handoff.png 1350w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>因此，提供可复制的属性值会是更好的办法，像其他交付工具如 Zeplin、蓝湖都是这么做的。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0ed70ce8837ec15f9e4d248b899ecfad/cf98e/zeplin.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Zeplin 右侧提供一个个属性值\"\n        title=\"Zeplin 右侧提供一个个属性值\"\n        src=\"/static/0ed70ce8837ec15f9e4d248b899ecfad/c08c5/zeplin.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0ed70ce8837ec15f9e4d248b899ecfad/0913d/zeplin.jpg 160w,\n/static/0ed70ce8837ec15f9e4d248b899ecfad/cb69c/zeplin.jpg 320w,\n/static/0ed70ce8837ec15f9e4d248b899ecfad/c08c5/zeplin.jpg 640w,\n/static/0ed70ce8837ec15f9e4d248b899ecfad/6a068/zeplin.jpg 960w,\n/static/0ed70ce8837ec15f9e4d248b899ecfad/eea4a/zeplin.jpg 1280w,\n/static/0ed70ce8837ec15f9e4d248b899ecfad/cf98e/zeplin.jpg 2150w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>其次则是 Figma 的访问速度问题，因为服务器在国外所以首次打开会很慢。设计师因为经常使用在本地有缓存或许还能忍受，但如果开发第一次收到这个链接花了好几分钟才打开，是万万不能接受的。</p>\n<p>由于这两个原因，加上受到 <a href=\"https://github.com/utom/sketch-measure\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sketch Measure</a> 的启发，我决定自己开发一个可以生成离线文件的 Figma 交付工具。它就叫 <a href=\"https://figmacn.com/handoff/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Figma handoff</a>，代码已经<a href=\"https://github.com/leadream/figma-handoff\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">开源在 GitHub</a>。</p>\n<p>下面，我想从功能的角度介绍一下 Figma handoff。</p>\n<h2>标注</h2>\n<p>Figma 与其他设计工具最大的不同是基于 Web 的属性，所有设计数据都存储于云端。因此，Figma handoff 是通过 Figma 提供的开放 API 来获取设计数据，来生成设计标注的。</p>\n<p>你只需要输入文件链接和 <a href=\"https://www.figma.com/developers/api#access-tokens\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Access Token</a>，并选择需要生成标注的 Frame，它就可以自动帮你生成标注了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/07a2ad8b0d97a0f86692766f9897e5f4/8449d/entry.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"开始生成标注\"\n        title=\"开始生成标注\"\n        src=\"/static/07a2ad8b0d97a0f86692766f9897e5f4/c08c5/entry.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/07a2ad8b0d97a0f86692766f9897e5f4/0913d/entry.jpg 160w,\n/static/07a2ad8b0d97a0f86692766f9897e5f4/cb69c/entry.jpg 320w,\n/static/07a2ad8b0d97a0f86692766f9897e5f4/c08c5/entry.jpg 640w,\n/static/07a2ad8b0d97a0f86692766f9897e5f4/6a068/entry.jpg 960w,\n/static/07a2ad8b0d97a0f86692766f9897e5f4/eea4a/entry.jpg 1280w,\n/static/07a2ad8b0d97a0f86692766f9897e5f4/8449d/entry.jpg 2006w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>基本信息标注</h3>\n<p>生成后的标注可以查看 Frame 和组件的尺寸、间距等信息，也可以查看每一个设计元素的各项属性。右侧的属性值都是可以直接点击复制的，方便开发根据自己的代码偏好使用。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6c104b2c3c3704d4eab88d5aa7b63cc0/de062/overview.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"界面一览\"\n        title=\"界面一览\"\n        src=\"/static/6c104b2c3c3704d4eab88d5aa7b63cc0/c08c5/overview.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6c104b2c3c3704d4eab88d5aa7b63cc0/0913d/overview.jpg 160w,\n/static/6c104b2c3c3704d4eab88d5aa7b63cc0/cb69c/overview.jpg 320w,\n/static/6c104b2c3c3704d4eab88d5aa7b63cc0/c08c5/overview.jpg 640w,\n/static/6c104b2c3c3704d4eab88d5aa7b63cc0/6a068/overview.jpg 960w,\n/static/6c104b2c3c3704d4eab88d5aa7b63cc0/eea4a/overview.jpg 1280w,\n/static/6c104b2c3c3704d4eab88d5aa7b63cc0/de062/overview.jpg 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>标注设置</h3>\n<p>同时，Figma handoff 还提供平台、像素密度、标注倍数和单位等选项，方便开发直接使用而不必换算。<strong>为了适应国内的微信生态，单位中还特别增加了小程序的 <code>rpx</code>。</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c9e631598e304b0074c2a493ed8e3821/70aca/settings.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"标注设置\"\n        title=\"标注设置\"\n        src=\"/static/c9e631598e304b0074c2a493ed8e3821/c08c5/settings.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c9e631598e304b0074c2a493ed8e3821/0913d/settings.jpg 160w,\n/static/c9e631598e304b0074c2a493ed8e3821/cb69c/settings.jpg 320w,\n/static/c9e631598e304b0074c2a493ed8e3821/c08c5/settings.jpg 640w,\n/static/c9e631598e304b0074c2a493ed8e3821/6a068/settings.jpg 960w,\n/static/c9e631598e304b0074c2a493ed8e3821/70aca/settings.jpg 966w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>样式标注</h3>\n<p>除了元素标注，Figma handoff 还会自动抓取当前文件中的样式，并生成对应的样式属性值，这些样式属性可以方便开发统一编写为 design tokens。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/790d499edc264c19b8ee6ae203913e02/e5166/style.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 88.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"样式面板\"\n        title=\"样式面板\"\n        src=\"/static/790d499edc264c19b8ee6ae203913e02/c08c5/style.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/790d499edc264c19b8ee6ae203913e02/0913d/style.jpg 160w,\n/static/790d499edc264c19b8ee6ae203913e02/cb69c/style.jpg 320w,\n/static/790d499edc264c19b8ee6ae203913e02/c08c5/style.jpg 640w,\n/static/790d499edc264c19b8ee6ae203913e02/6a068/style.jpg 960w,\n/static/790d499edc264c19b8ee6ae203913e02/e5166/style.jpg 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>富文本样式</h3>\n<p>这里需要特别提一下富文本样式的标注。我们在设计时有一些文本图层包含多种样式，为了方便查看这种富文本样式，我将文本进行了分段，开发可以点击对应的文本段来查看不同文字片段的各项属性值。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/832f79d263f769acc17314e611ad3fdb/fcb1e/multiple-styles.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"富文本样式\"\n        title=\"富文本样式\"\n        src=\"/static/832f79d263f769acc17314e611ad3fdb/c08c5/multiple-styles.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/832f79d263f769acc17314e611ad3fdb/0913d/multiple-styles.jpg 160w,\n/static/832f79d263f769acc17314e611ad3fdb/cb69c/multiple-styles.jpg 320w,\n/static/832f79d263f769acc17314e611ad3fdb/c08c5/multiple-styles.jpg 640w,\n/static/832f79d263f769acc17314e611ad3fdb/6a068/multiple-styles.jpg 960w,\n/static/832f79d263f769acc17314e611ad3fdb/eea4a/multiple-styles.jpg 1280w,\n/static/832f79d263f769acc17314e611ad3fdb/fcb1e/multiple-styles.jpg 1452w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>离线下载</h2>\n<p>前文说过，Figma 在国内的访问速度不是很快，因此 Figma handoff 提供了离线下载模式，也就是将生成的设计标注下载为一个本地网页，这样给开发之后也就不存在速度慢的问题了。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5da4e5b5fc22e2e876a7b69991c39484/9d6a9/offline-download.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"离线下载标注\"\n        title=\"离线下载标注\"\n        src=\"/static/5da4e5b5fc22e2e876a7b69991c39484/6af66/offline-download.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5da4e5b5fc22e2e876a7b69991c39484/69538/offline-download.png 160w,\n/static/5da4e5b5fc22e2e876a7b69991c39484/72799/offline-download.png 320w,\n/static/5da4e5b5fc22e2e876a7b69991c39484/6af66/offline-download.png 640w,\n/static/5da4e5b5fc22e2e876a7b69991c39484/d9199/offline-download.png 960w,\n/static/5da4e5b5fc22e2e876a7b69991c39484/21b4d/offline-download.png 1280w,\n/static/5da4e5b5fc22e2e876a7b69991c39484/9d6a9/offline-download.png 2256w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>但是，由于设计数据是直接通过 API 从 Figma 服务器获取的，所以在生成离线标注时可能会遇到导出比较慢的情况。这种情况下推荐使用科学上网并开启全局代理以加快速度，当然你也可以选择一部分 Frame 导出，而不是一次性导出整个文件的标注。</p>\n<h2>切图</h2>\n<p>在设计交付中切图也一直是一个令人头疼的问题。Figma 的右侧面板中有 Export 属性，具有查看权限的用户可以任意选择格式、后缀和倍数来导出所选元素。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b44f7abc91c8346191938b88db65af69/12bff/export-settings.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Export 设置\"\n        title=\"Export 设置\"\n        src=\"/static/b44f7abc91c8346191938b88db65af69/6af66/export-settings.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b44f7abc91c8346191938b88db65af69/69538/export-settings.png 160w,\n/static/b44f7abc91c8346191938b88db65af69/72799/export-settings.png 320w,\n/static/b44f7abc91c8346191938b88db65af69/6af66/export-settings.png 640w,\n/static/b44f7abc91c8346191938b88db65af69/d9199/export-settings.png 960w,\n/static/b44f7abc91c8346191938b88db65af69/12bff/export-settings.png 1032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>一般来说，设计师可以邀请开发查看文件，自己按需导出素材，但是由于开发往往对设计师的文件结构不了解，容易导出错误的切图。因此，我建议设计师自己负责切图，根据开发的要求在文件中设置好 Export 属性，Figma handoff 可以自动识别到所有带有 Export 的元素，生成切图。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a1bae9faa904ed61b94526a558b03afa/614df/exports.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"切图\"\n        title=\"切图\"\n        src=\"/static/a1bae9faa904ed61b94526a558b03afa/c08c5/exports.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a1bae9faa904ed61b94526a558b03afa/0913d/exports.jpg 160w,\n/static/a1bae9faa904ed61b94526a558b03afa/cb69c/exports.jpg 320w,\n/static/a1bae9faa904ed61b94526a558b03afa/c08c5/exports.jpg 640w,\n/static/a1bae9faa904ed61b94526a558b03afa/6a068/exports.jpg 960w,\n/static/a1bae9faa904ed61b94526a558b03afa/614df/exports.jpg 978w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>最后</h2>\n<p>我差不多花了三个月的时间写出了这个交付工具，主要还是想让 Figma 的设计交付更加方便，让更多还在犹豫的设计师可以大胆放心地开始使用 Figma。</p>\n<p>Figma handoff 整个设计和开发的过程都是由我一人完成，这中间也邀请了一些设计师朋友帮忙内测，并在他们的不断反馈之下打磨细节，再次感谢他们。如果你在使用时有任何问题，也可以在 <a href=\"https://github.com/leadream/figma-handoff/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GitHub issues</a> 中告诉我。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"为了让更多人用上 Figma，我做了一个设计交付工具","date":"2020/02/13","description":"让 Figma 交付变得简单。","color":"#111421","cover":"figma-handoff.png","demo":"https://figmacn.com/handoff","demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/figma-handoff/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tutorial/how-to-make-a-boring-figma-plugin/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"怎样写一个有趣但无用的 Figma 插件？"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/thoughts/designer-developer-handoff/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"聊聊设计交付这件事"}}}}}